                <p>This gives your team the freedom to problem-solve and the responsibility to follow through.</p>
                
                <p>Control isn't about doing the jobâ€”it's about clearly defining the win and letting your people run with it.</p>

                <h2>Phase 4: Build in Feedback Loops That Train Continuously</h2>
                <p>Accountability isn't about catching people doing things wrong. It's about growing their awareness so they improve with every rep.</p>
                
                <p>Here's a simple feedback loop structure we recommend:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Ask: "What worked? What didn't?"</li>
